444
00:41:47,508 --> 00:41:53,089
<font color="#616161">Fame is a fickle friend, Harry. Celebrity is as celebrity does.</font>

445
00:41:54,056 --> 00:41:55,974
<font color="#616161">Remember that.</font>

446
00:41:59,728 --> 00:42:01,897
<font color="#616161">Come.</font>

