548
00:50:10,260 --> 00:50:12,513
<font color="#616161">Now, according to legend....</font>

549
00:50:12,679 --> 00:50:16,391
<font color="#616161">....Slytherin had built a hidden chamber in this castle....</font>

550
00:50:16,558 --> 00:50:20,229
<font color="#616161">....known as the
Chamber of Secrets.</font>

551
00:50:20,395 --> 00:50:24,817
